column5: The same thing happen to me, sometimes I wish to get hit by a car so I would know who would get actually worried and not, and in the extreme cases I want to die but to really know who would ever miss me

I cant say that I know how do you feel right now, because probably no one knows, but if I'm sure of something in this life its that it isn't fair, I know this comment wont mean anything to you but for the big man up there, which I don't believe either, I hope you don't do any stupidity like taking your own life because I don't know you but just reading this made me care about you, I hope your situation gets better some day for you
